description: Export Android resources in Sketch. Support bitmap, vector, nine-patch, app icon, shape XML and color.

s2v_version_message:
Run follow command in the Terminal.
$ sudo npm update -g svg2vectordrawable
install_s2v_title: Please check that you have svg2vectordrawable installed.
install_s2v_message:
Export Android vector drawable feature depend on Node.js and svg2vectordrawable.
After you installed Node.js, run follow command in the Terminal.
$ sudo npm install -g svg2vectordrawable
